name: City of Bishop Park
description: City of Bishop Park is a place to play pickleball in Bishop, CA. There are 4 outdoor hard courts. The lines are permanent, and portable nets are available. The courts are free. Players have access to restrooms, water, and lights.

name: Fredonia AZ High School Gym
description: Fredonia AZ High School Gym is a place to play pickleball in Parklabrea, CA. There are 3 indoor asphalt courts. The lines are permanent, and portable nets are available. A one-time fee is required to play. Amenities include restrooms and water.
